text.tspan: Red Rose was designed by Jaikishan Patel and released in
2018 by his independently owned and operated company,
MagicType, in Mumbai, India. Red Rose is an exclusively
designed Latin typeface, inspired by the Serifs typeface. Its
distinguishing factors are its triangular-shaped serif design
and curved strokes near the end of the axes. I was drawn to
Red Rose because of its unique flared character strokes and
